<BLOCK2><TI>345 King</TI>
<P><BOLD>39.</BOLD> The APS dated March 20, 2006 for 345 King Street, Waterloo provided for a closing date of October 26, 2006. At some point, Schembri negotiated a vendor takeback mortgage in the amount of $99,000 (the <BOLD>&ldquo;Schade VTB&rdquo;)</BOLD>. Based on the payout statement for the Schade VTB dated May 9, 2007, I believe that Schembri extended the closing date. I do not know the date that Schembri completed, through his father, the acquisition of this property. A copy of the Schade VTB payout statement is attached hereto and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;5&rdquo;</BOLD>.</P></BLOCK2>
