<P><BOLD>81.</BOLD> I do not know the amounts Schembri paid in connection with carrying 345 King and 344 Spruce (eg. mortgage payments to TD and RBC, and property insurance). However, I do know that such payments did not include property taxes as 172 paid the outstanding property taxes on 345 King and 344 Spruce when it acquired these properties from Schembri's father (as appears in the trust ledger statements forming part of Exhibit &ldquo;21&rdquo;).</P>
<P><BOLD>82.</BOLD> I do not know the amounts Schembri paid in connection with developing the JV Lands (eg. Phase One assessments for 345 King and 344 Spruce, and site plan fee(s) paid to the City). However, I do know that such payments did not include the services rendered by Schembri's consultants; namely:
