<P><BOLD>123.</BOLD> There are several errors and omissions in Schembri's evidence in paragraphs 62 to 66 of the Schembri April 2010 Affidavit; certain of which are as follows:
<P1>(a) Mapleton Flooring supplied the laminate, not The Source;</P1>
<P1>(b) Schembri's purported retention of Mike's Hardwood Flooring fails to mention that the purchase order provided that Mike's would only transfer the laminate material to the units after the laminate material had been carried and placed on each floor of the 14-story building; leaving it to James way to do so;</P1>
<P1>(c) Schembri omits the fact that there were other flooring materials supplied and installed; and</P1>
<P1>(d) Schembri omits the fact that Schembri Custom Kitchens failed to carry the kitchen cabinets from outside the building (where they were delivered) to each and every one of the units in the 14-story building (where they were to be installed); leaving it to Jamesway to do so.</P1></P>
