<P><BOLD>181.</BOLD> The sole business and purpose of Simcoe &amp; Eastwood was to design, construct and sell a student housing development on the Oshawa Lands. The preliminary budget to develop the Oshawa Lands was $12,000,000.</P></BLOCK1>
