<P><BOLD>223.</BOLD> I asked questions about those variances while circling the corresponding amounts in our summary. One of the questions I asked related to the incomplete listing of change orders in the KPMG summary, which amounted to a total variance of approximately $330,000. Schembri responded by saying he approved of change orders for the subs but not for any of my companies. Schembri pre-empted further discussion by grabbing the KPMG summary out of my hand and terminating the meeting.</P>
<P><BOLD>224.</BOLD> Copies of documents relating to the involvement of KPMG are attached hereto and marked as <BOLD>Exhibit &ldquo;99&rdquo;.</BOLD></P></BLOCK1>
