<P><BOLD>327.</BOLD> I was also informed by Cole and believed that Wortzman represented that Schembri would be bringing a motion for summary judgment in the ROFR Action (the <BOLD>&ldquo;Purported Schembri ROFR SJ Motion&rdquo;).</BOLD></P>
