<P><BOLD>359.</BOLD> I have subsequently come to believe that Schembri was attempting to bankrupt me so he would not have to comply with the Contribution Clause and ROFR Clause. I come to believe this, in part, following a telephone call from Erich Mallet, of CIBC, wherein he inquired who Schembri was Schembri had contacted CIBC and bad-mouthed me.</P>
