<P>The Defendants will make a Motion to the Honourable Mr. Justice Sloan on Thursday, February 8, 2018 at 10:00 a.m., or as soon after that time as the Motion can be heard at the court house, 85 Frederick Street, Kitchener, Ontario, N2H 0A7.</P>
